</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-66_ pf-text-1"><strong>Regular refresher courses</strong> - To ensure first aid skills and knowledge are current, refresher courses should be undertaken at least every three years.




































