</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-77_ pf-text-1"><strong>Allergies </strong>- With the rise in childhood allergies, promptly recognising and treating allergic reactions is a critical skill.





































</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-79_ pf-text-1"><strong>Injury prevention</strong> - Training should also cover preventive measures to reduce injuries in early years settings.






































