</h3><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-96_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">To enhance the effectiveness of first aid training in early years, it is recommended that:



























</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-98_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-99_ pf-text-1"><strong>All staff are trained </strong>- Beyond the minimum requirement, all staff members should be trained in paediatric first aid.






































